<% layout('/layouts/boilerplate.ejs') -%>

    <div class="container mt-5 mb-5">
        <div class="privacy-card shadow p-5">

            <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Privacy Policy 🔒</h2>

            <p>
                At <b>Wanderlust</b>, we value your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and
                protect your information when you use our website.
            </p>

            <h4 class="mt-4">1. Information We Collect</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Personal information (name, email, account details)</li>
                <li>Booking details (check-in, check-out, pricing)</li>
                <li>Usage data (pages visited, interactions)</li>
            </ul>

            <h4 class="mt-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>To process bookings and payments</li>
                <li>To send booking confirmations and emails</li>
                <li>To improve user experience</li>
            </ul>

            <h4 class="mt-4">3. Data Protection</h4>
            <p>
                We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal data. However, no method of
                transmission over the internet is 100% secure.
            </p>

            <h4 class="mt-4">4. Third-Party Services</h4>
            <p>
                We may use third-party services like Cloudinary for image storage and email services for communication.
            </p>

            <h4 class="mt-4">5. Your Rights</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>You can update or delete your account</li>
                <li>You can request access to your data</li>
            </ul>

            <h4 class="mt-4">6. Changes to Policy</h4>
            <p>
                We may update this policy from time to time. Please review it periodically.
            </p>

            <h4 class="mt-4">7. Contact Us</h4>
            <p>
                If you have any questions, contact us at: <b>wanderlust@gmail.com</b>
            </p>
            
            <div class="text-center mt-4">
                <a href="/listings" class="btn btn-outline-dark">Back to Listings</a>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>